{"type":"message","id":"aa050de5","parentId":"827cffee","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:00:51.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the information I need. Tomorrow is Saturday, April 25th, 2026 (2026-04-25).\n\nFor the evening slot (programming topic), I need to find the topic for Saturday. \n\nLooking at `generateWeeklyPlan`, it maps days 0-6 (Monday-Sunday). Saturday is index 5.\n\nFor the evening programming topics (PROGRAMMING_TOPICS_EVENING), there are 7 topics:\n- Monday: binary-search\n- Tuesday: dp (dynamic-programming)\n- Wednesday: pointers\n- Thursday: closures\n- Friday: java-collections\n- Saturday: sorting\n\n\n- Sunday: bfs-dfs\n\nSo the Saturday topic is 'sorting'. I'm checking the TikTok scripts to see what's available—the existing scripts cover binary-search, pointers, dp, clean-code, and loops, but there's no specific script for 'sorting'. I'll need to handle this case when the generator runs.","thinkingSignature":"da273769c51753f9744559fb15ce0585968342206c20db5f1f0fcbc0c45db7b7"},{"type":"text","text":"Tomorrow is **Saturday, April 25, 2026**. The evening (programming) topic for Saturday is **sorting** (sorting algorithms). Let me run the generator.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c263vdixnjma_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/content-automation/generate-tiktok-content.mjs 2026-04-25 sorting 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2744,"output":309,"cacheRead":12745,"cacheWrite":503,"totalTokens":16301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776988839871,"responseId":"0639e5a82b49f3b67a227082e709cc7d"}}
